*    {Options}:  -p   Force Production server when running at Test.
*                -t   Force Test server when running at Production.
*                -m   Create folder on remote server.
*                -n   Do not convert UNIX EOL to Windows EOL format.
*                -D   Delete Local file after successful transfer.
*                -Z   Bypass transfer - testing (option -m still works).
